Kulobu bugebengu nokubulawa kwabantu esikubona nsuku zonke kwithelevishini nasemaphephandabeni kubulawa odadewethu, abafowethu nezihlobo ngabantu abaziwayo nabatholwa benamacala. Ngabe uhulumeni wethu ufuna kuze kwenzekeni kanti? Mina nginaso isisombululo kule nto, yisigwebo sentambo esiyisisombululo. Ngiyazi abaningi bazophikasana nami kulokhu bethi kwafa abantu abaningi ngendlela engafanele ngesikhatthi sobandlululo kodwa-ke njengoba besho kwakuyisikhathi sobandlululo, manje sekubusa uhulumeni wentando yabantu. Ake sibukele komakhelwane bethu abafana neBotswana. Sikhona isigwebo sentambo futhi uma uqhathanisa izinga lobugebengu nelethu la eMzansi izibalo zikhomba ukuthi eBotswana liphansi kakhulu. Ukubopha umuntu otholwe kunesiqiniseko sokuthi udlwengulile waphinde wabulala izingane ezintathu emndenini akusizi ngalutho ngoba nasejele lapho wondliwa yimali yentela ekhokhwa uye lo muntu abulale izingane zakhe. Sekwanele manje ma-Afrika ngicela uhulumeni ayibukisise kahle le ndaba futhi nginesiqiniseko sokuthi ingabehlisa ubugebengu nokubulawa kwabantu.  Thokozani ELovu